All credit goes to
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/322108/?]AnTiWoMaAgNoT[/url] who created the mesh. The guy who created all those great statues, if you don't have them: download them
 only copied it a few times to replace all the different little rocks in skyrim and put a few textures to it.

[youtube][/youtube]

Info:
It's a new higher poly model for those 4 little rocks appearing in skyrim. They are also a bit bigger.
They probably will look a lot better with your system, as my old rig doesn't allow me using shadows on them.

My screens are made with recommended mods:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/42370/?]Unique Grasses and Groundcovers - Nature and Landscape Enhancement [/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54196/?]Unique Grasses and Groundcovers Plugin [/url]   that's the version with more stuff
